### 3. Novelty
Episodic vs. semantic memory distinction is classical (Tulving). Uncertainty-driven retrieval exists in active learning and meta-learning. The DNC and episodic control work cited show hybrid memory retrieval. The novelty here is the specific formalization of an entropy-threshold rule for LM agents in text games. This is a reasonable synthesis/adaptation rather than a fundamental innovation—it applies known principles to a specific context.

